sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant FE as React Frontend
  participant API as Backend API
  participant PG as Payment Gateway
  participant DB as Database

  U->>FE: 강의 선택 및 신청 정보 입력
  FE->>API: POST /api/orders
  API->>DB: 주문 pending 생성
  API-->>FE: orderId, amount, orderName
  FE->>PG: 결제창 호출
  PG-->>FE: successUrl(paymentKey, orderId, amount)
  FE->>API: POST /api/payments/confirm
  API->>DB: 주문 금액/상태 조회
  API->>PG: 결제 승인 API 호출
  PG-->>API: 승인 결과
  API->>DB: orders paid, payments approved, enrollment confirmed
  API-->>FE: 신청 완료
  FE-->>U: 완료 화면 표시
